snippet.title: Godzilla x Kong : The New Empire | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witness the rise of a new empire. #GodzillaXKong - Only in theaters 2024

The epic battle continues!  Legendary Picturesâ€™ cinematic Monsterverse follows up the explosive showdown of â€œGodzilla vs. Kongâ€ with an all-new adventure that pits the almighty Kong and the fearsome Godzilla against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existenceâ€”and our own. â€œGodzilla x Kong: The New Empireâ€ delves further into the histories of these Titans and their origins, as well as the mysteries of Skull Island and beyond, while uncovering the mythic battle that helped forge these extraordinary beings and tied them to humankind forever.

Once again at the helm is director Adam Wingard.  The film stars Rebecca Hall (â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ The Night Houseâ€), Brian Tyree Henry (â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ â€œBullet Trainâ€), Dan Stevens (â€œGaslit,â€ â€œLegion,â€ â€œBeauty and the Beastâ€), Kaylee Hottle (â€œGodzilla vs. Kongâ€), Alex Ferns (â€œThe Batman,â€ â€œWrath of Man,â€ â€œChernobylâ€) and Fala Chen (â€œIrma Vep,â€ â€œShang Chi and the Legend of the Ten Ringsâ€).

The screenplay is by Terry Rossio (â€œGodzilla vs. Kongâ€ the â€œPirates of the Caribbeanâ€ series) and Simon Barrett (â€œYouâ€™re Nextâ€) and Jeremy Slater (â€œMoon Knightâ€), from a story by Rossio & Wingard & Barrett, based on the character â€œGodzillaâ€ owned and created by TOHO Co., Ltd..  The film is produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric Mcleod, Thomas Tull, Jon Jashni and Brian Rogers.  The executive producers are Wingard, Jen Conroy, Jay Ashenfelter, Yoshimitsu Banno, Kenji Okuhira. 

Once again, Wingard is collaborating with director of photography Ben Seresin (â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ â€œWorld War Zâ€), production designer Tom Hammock (â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ â€œX,â€ â€œThe Guestâ€), editor Josh Schaeffer (â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ â€œMollyâ€™s Gameâ€), costume designer Emily Seresin (â€œThe Invisible Man,â€ â€œTop of the Lakeâ€).  The composers are Tom Holkenborg (â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ â€œMad Max: Fury Roadâ€) and Antonio Di Iorio (additional music on â€œGodzilla vs. Kong,â€ the â€œSonic the Hedgehogâ€ films).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, â€œGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire.â€  It is slated for release nationwide only in theaters and IMAX on April 12, 2024 and beginning 10 April 2024 internationally, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures except in Japan, where the film will be distributed by Toho Co., Ltd and in mainland China, where it will be distributed by Legendary East.

snippet.title: Dating Mausi Ki Student - Stand Up Comedy by Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi (Crowd Work Video)
snippet.description:
Hello Doston,

Presenting a new Stand Up Comedy crowd work video:
Dating Mausi Ki Student which was recorded in my comedy show called BEST OF GUPTAJI.

This is a New Stand Up Comedy video which we have recorded in October at The Comedy Theatre, Gurgoan

Hope you enjoy this latest comedy video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai and Genuinely, I am presenting my new show with an old name Best of GuptaJi which I am starting to tour now.
Why Best of GuptaJi? because I want all the content in my show to be the best content from my side. So if you have seen my videos on chai, maggi, hotel, airport, tinder, starbucks etc, it was a part of Best of GuptaJi only so am trying to give you new content but with that level only.

If you want to come for the Best of GuptaJi tour, here is the ticket link : https://linktr.ee/appurvgupta

Book Now as we have limited seats in every city.

snippet.title: 99 Details From the GTA 6 Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't miss our GTA 6 trailer breakdown! The GTA 6 trailer is finally here and we've looked over the entire footage and uncovered 99 hidden and hard to find details littered throughout our first look at GTA VI.

There are lots of cool new things to pick out from this brand new Grand Theft Auto 6 trailer from Rockstar Games, and in our GTA 6 trailer deep dive, we examine clues about GTA 6 map locations, hints about the GTA 6 world, glimpses of what might happen in the GTA 6 story, references to GTA Vice City, and more.

The GTA 6 release date is 2025 on PS5 and Xbox Series X/S.

Credit to tachyon_v for the map creation 

For more on Grand Theft Auto VI, check out our GTA 6 trailer reaction video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PuMSEkVqC9k

Episode 3946: Daya Ka Intezaar
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal discovers that he has been lying about Daya's homecoming, he strikes Sundar with a bamboo stick. Sundar runs, but Jetha pursues after him. Champaklal shouts at Sundar and admits that Daya did not return because her mother did not want her to leave the house during the auspicious Diwali season. Later, Jethalal and Tapu inquire about Daya's ultimate arrival date with Sundar.

snippet.title: CID cast Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava at crematorium for last rites of late actor Dinesh Phadnis
snippet.description:
CID cast members Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava, Tanya Abrol, and Ansha Sayed gathered at the crematorium to pay their respects to the late actor Dinesh Phadnis, who passed away last night. His last rites took place at Daulat Nagar crematorium in Borivali around 10:30-11 am. The actor, who battled for his life, succumbed around 12 am after being admitted to Tunga Hospital in Mumbai. ETimes TV got to speak with the actors, who shared their fond memories.

snippet.title: Bobby Deol Interview | â€˜Always knew Animal will workâ€™ | Ranbir Kapoor | Gadar 2 | Dharmendra
snippet.description:
In a candid chat with Pinkvilla, Bobby Deol opens up about the historic success of Animal, the bond with Ranbir Kapoor on the sets, and the vision of director Sandeep Reddy Vanga. The actor decodes his iconic entry scene and speaks from his heart about the success tasted by brother Sunny Deol and father Dharmendra in 2023 with Gadar 2 and Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani. Bobby also gives an update on Soldier 2, Animal 2 and Apne 2 and explains what would it take for him to come on board a comedy. Watch Video.

Bhide's "Suvichaar" or thought of the day states that anger, pain, and agony are a waste of energy and time so people should avoid engaging themselves in these. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
